    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on longevity, including a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed VANOS system to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise throws, sending power to the rear wheels through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to upgraded polyurethane bushings and a tuned suspension setup that maintains excellent lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain exhibits exceptional compression and linear power delivery across the entire rev range. A true driver\u2019s specimen for those who value mechanical pedigree and analog feedback.",
