    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy luster, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a light surface scratch near the trunk lid\u2014imperfections that are consistent with careful use. The alloy wheels are in great shape with only minimal curb rash on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is clean and has been kept smoke-free. The leather seating is firm and supportive, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, while the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All electronic features, including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and sunroof, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, recently completing a full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection that confirmed the suspension and exhaust systems are in solid working order. The tires provide excellent grip with approximately 70% tread life remaining. This car drives straight and true, offering a smooth, rattle-free experience that confirms its mechanical integrity. It is ready for the road today with no immediate service required.",
